AsteroidDB
━━━━━━━━━━
Contains the final snapshot of the D. Bolton Asteroids source code, as seen in Chapter 48, from the Ebook:
	https://www.amazon.co.uk/Learn-C-Games-Programming-Beginners-ebook/dp/B07MZG5H29/ref=sr_1_3?s=digital-text&ie=UTF8&qid=1548195742&sr=1-3&keywords=learn+c+programming

There is now a blog about C and Games programming and accompanying the book at:
	https://learncgames.com/

The original source files are asteroids_ch48.zip and LICENSE (as well as information contained in its README), under
	https://github.com/David-H-Bolton/LearnC
